00:40:29,700 --> 00:40:31,700
What should I do?

507
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:34,000
What is it now?

508
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:38,640
In the operating room just now, you once again risked your life to protect me.

509
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:41,960
Tell me.

510
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:46,960
I owe a girl two lives, so how should I pay her back?

511
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:50,080
This wasn't the case, don't overthink it.

512
00:40:50,080 --> 00:40:54,540
You stepped in front of a gun for me. Can I not overthink it?

513
00:40:54,540 --> 00:40:59,460
Just now, you told the Health Commission's representative

514
00:40:59,460 --> 00:41:04,460
that I was your idol and you're willing to die for me.

515
00:41:04,460 --> 00:41:07,260
 Idol?

516
