When did I say something like that? Don’t pretend to understand.

518
00:41:16,060 --> 00:41:22,400
You didn't say that? Then maybe I heard the voice of your heart.

519
00:41:32,940 --> 00:41:34,740
Su Wei'an.

520
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:40,960
Don't joke with your life anymore.

521
