523
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:56,780
Exchanging my life for yours is worth it.

524
00:41:56,780 --> 00:42:00,700
I told you. Don't say such things again.

525
00:42:00,700 --> 00:42:05,180
No one's life is more valuable than someone else's.

526
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:16,160
W-Wait a minute.

527
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:24,360
